  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/f1cef842cf672f3117cc93db0babe4ab.poster.avif?t=1754556447\" width=616 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/f1cef842cf672f3117cc93db0babe4ab.webm?t=1754556447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><i><strong>Block'Em!</strong></i> is an action-filled block-building party game for <strong>2 to 4 players</strong>! <br>The controls are simple but the road to victory is complex.<br>Be the first to reach the goal or be the last Blocky standing!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/f0d935d38cfafec189c086ee913df64b.avif?t=1754556447\" width=616 height=133 /></span><br><br>Cute, addictive and fast paced party game to be enjoyed by 2-4 players.<br>Outsmarting your opponent with cunning moves is easier said than done!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/5b8e2734475f3409c0ad8fd9a5605a37.poster.avif?t=1754556447\" width=562 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/5b8e2734475f3409c0ad8fd9a5605a37.webm?t=1754556447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/5b8e2734475f3409c0ad8fd9a5605a37.mp4?t=1754556447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/e3906d84293fc758715c6f9ec3469e9a.avif?t=1754556447\" width=616 height=133 /></span><br><br>An exciting mix of platform and puzzle!<br>Find your way through the vibrant, chaotic arena. Watch out for the fireballs!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/c754164e52739dd2b9b5c18caa756607.poster.avif?t=1754556447\" width=562 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/c754164e52739dd2b9b5c18caa756607.webm?t=1754556447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/c754164e52739dd2b9b5c18caa756607.mp4?t=1754556447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/7a0f9759cedda12f4a4122dc1d48dd6c.avif?t=1754556447\" width=616 height=133 /></span><br><br>Block’Em brings out your competitive side.<br>A sure way to make friendships stronger… or not!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/1751985bea81804b91b6715d00acfe0c.poster.avif?t=1754556447\" width=562 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/1751985bea81804b91b6715d00acfe0c.webm?t=1754556447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/1751985bea81804b91b6715d00acfe0c.mp4?t=1754556447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/a5024444db12f12924496318903bc8f6.avif?t=1754556447\" width=616 height=133 /></span><br><br>Beat your opponents in a race to the finish or be the last Block to survive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/ed61f85764c8bbe1f9eeed3f41f0d2c6.poster.avif?t=1754556447\" width=562 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/ed61f85764c8bbe1f9eeed3f41f0d2c6.webm?t=1754556447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/ed61f85764c8bbe1f9eeed3f41f0d2c6.mp4?t=1754556447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1529220/extras/95f8b8f1ca83f761746d733e3a38408f.avif?t=1754556447\" width=616 height=133 /></span><br><br>Eat. Sleep. Block’Em. Repeat.",
